        "subject": "LU-4668 autoconf: restore LIBCFS_FUNC_DUMP_TRACE test",
        "message": "LU-4668 autoconf: restore LIBCFS_FUNC_DUMP_TRACE test\n\nLIBCFS_FUNC_DUMP_TRACE test was removed from\ncommit 8250f49e3d0431db6a6363f959d2cce65684c74e because\ndump_trace has been upstream since v2.6.23. However,\nit's not supported by powerpc arch. This patch restores\nthe test so as to make Lustre codes work on powerpc.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jian Yu <jian.yu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I76b843770b78163163a9c99a38967a0e1ea5ab68\n"
